&lt;li&gt;CTS (Certified Technology Specialist) certification or willingness to obtain it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Crestron, Extron, Q-SYS, Biamp, or Shure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AutoCAD or Microsoft Visio.&lt;/

